headline: SLB Awarded Multi-Year Contracts to Support Oman’s Energy Development
summary: HOUSTON, January 28, 2026--SLB (NYSE: SLB) has been awarded two five-year contracts by Petroleum Development Oman (PDO) to supply wellheads and artificial lift technologies for operations in Block-6, Oman’s largest oil and gas concession, while advancing in-country value (ICV).

headline: Cruz Battery Metals Enters into Joint Venture Agreement for Deep Basin Lithium Brine Exploration in Clayton Valley, Nevada
summary: Vancouver, British Columbia--(Newsfile Corp. - January 28, 2026) - Cruz Battery Metals Corp. (CSE: CRUZ) (OTCID: BKTPF) (WKN: A40YSN) ("Cruz" or the "Company") is pleased to announce that it has entered into a joint venture agreement ("JV") with Sienna Resources Inc. ("Sienna") and Adelayde Exploration Inc. ("Adelayde") to explore the deep basin lithium brine potential in Clayton Valley, Nevada.
